================================================================================
Model weights
================================================================================

The default local embedding model is `intfloat/multilingual-e5-small`, fetched
on demand by `@huggingface/transformers` into `SSTICKER_MODEL_CACHE` when the
operator runs `ssticker models pull` or the first request that needs it.

- Model: intfloat/multilingual-e5-small
- Source: https://huggingface.co/intfloat/multilingual-e5-small
- License: MIT
- Required acknowledgement: see https://huggingface.co/intfloat/multilingual-e5-small

If you change `SSTICKER_MODEL_ID`, consult the replacement model card and
update this NOTICE accordingly.

================================================================================
Third-party notices
================================================================================

A complete list of bundled direct dependencies and their licenses is generated
into `THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md` by `pnpm run licenses:generate`. CI runs
`pnpm run licenses:check` to fail the build if that file drifts from the
locked dependency graph.
